recentReportStory.title: Muzarabani holds nerve to give Zimbabwe thrilling tie
recentReportStory.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Scotland, World Cup qualifier, Bulawayo
recentReportStory.seoTitle: Muzarabani holds nerve to give Zimbabwe thrilling tie
recentReportStory.summary: With one to defend off the last over, the seamer started with a wide but then had Scotland's No. 11 Brad Wheal caught behind with his next delivery to spark wild celebrations
recentReportStory.byline: The Report by Liam Brickhill in Bulawayo

image.caption: Safyaan Sharif celebrates Hamilton Masakadza's wicket
image.longCaption: Safyaan Sharif celebrates Hamilton Masakadza's wicket, Scotland v Zimbabwe, World Cup Qualifier 2018, Bulawayo, March 11, 2018

recentReportStory.credit: Liam Brickhill is a freelance journalist based in Cape Town
